text: Michiels in 2018 Githa Michiels (born 28 March 1983) is a Belgian cross- country cyclist. She placed 21st in the women's cross-country race at the 2016 Summer Olympics. She was on the start list of 2018 Cross-Country European Championships and finished 3rd.. ==References== Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Belgian female cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Belgium Category:Cyclists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp
